Responsibilities:

  Assist in the development of media releases and other media materials to support the publicity efforts of the agency
  Assist in the organisation and management of media events
  Assist in social media listening and media monitoring for compilation into Daily News Briefs
  Assist in research and prep work for Media Assessment reports
  Any other support required for the smooth running and execution of the department's communications and stakeholder engagement work

Other Information:

  The duration of the traineeship is 6 months
